686
00:39:56,251 --> 00:39:58,623
Look how you're holding her.

687
00:39:59,496 --> 00:40:01,009
A baby girl.

688
00:40:02,794 --> 00:40:04,566
It's all over now.

689
00:40:08,227 --> 00:40:09,449
I know.

690
00:40:15,146 --> 00:40:16,620
I have to find him.

